parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Corrosion of the Subframe and Crossmember
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the subframe and crossmember can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle's steering wheel becomes loose

and the lower control arm breaks
causing the vehicle to lose control.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Inadequate Repair and Maintenance of Recalled Vehicles
